      "id": "no-wonder-you-re-stuck-you-keep-strengthening-what-weakens-you",
      "title": "No wonder you’re stuck. You keep strengthening what weakens you.",
      "body": "<div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"1jt60-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><img src=\"/img/ideas/1782545179341-2BB2D0AB-9457-49C8-8DB9-67C685E13A0C.JPG\" alt=\"2BB2D0AB-9457-49C8-8DB9-67C685E13A0C.JPG\"><div data-offset-key=\"1jt60-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"1jt60-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">The hard part is that it did help.\nIt showed you what wasn’t working.\nBut then you kept feeding it\nuntil it took more from you than it gave.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"2tc8h-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"2tc8h-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"2tc8h-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">It usually starts with something small enough to defend.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"8e24c-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"8e24c-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"8e24c-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">One bad set.\nOne weak attempt.\nOne slow result.\nOne missed standard.\nOne night where you fell back into the same pattern and couldn’t pretend you didn’t notice.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"1h8dq-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"1h8dq-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"1h8dq-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">That hit isn’t useless.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"cibn3-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"cibn3-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"cibn3-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">It shows you something.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"apun0-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"apun0-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"apun0-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">Where the setup was weak. Where you rushed. Where you stopped paying attention. Where you avoided the rep. Where you tolerated something that had already started costing you.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"3762q-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"3762q-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"3762q-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">That kind of pain can be useful when it sends you back sharper.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"2bh5t-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"2bh5t-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"2bh5t-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">You change the setup.\nFix the weak point.\nStudy what broke.\nHandle the next attempt differently.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"iife-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"iife-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"iife-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">That’s the job of the warning.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"53flv-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"53flv-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"53flv-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">It puts a spotlight on something that needs attention.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"8c24u-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"8c24u-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"8c24u-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">It’s supposed to help you change what happens next.\nIt’s not supposed to become the place you keep returning to.</span></span></div></div><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-16dba41\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; border: 0px solid black; color: rgb(231, 233, 234); display: inline; font-width: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; list-style: none; position: relative; overflow-wrap: break-word; min-width: 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2;\"><h1 class=\"longform-header-one-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"943hv-0-0\" style=\"font-size: calc(21px); line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px;\"><div data-offset-key=\"943hv-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"943hv-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">Then you kept feeding it</span></span></div></h1></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"6llu0-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"6llu0-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"6llu0-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">The problem starts after it’s already shown you enough.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"chfcr-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"chfcr-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"chfcr-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">You don’t just notice what went wrong. You check it again. You replay it at night. You wake up and build your morning around it. You let one bad sign become the tone of your whole day.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"ae9gl-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"ae9gl-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"ae9gl-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">You keep carrying what went wrong long after it has already shown you what needs to change.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"4skn4-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"4skn4-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"4skn4-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">Sometimes you call it staying honest.\nSometimes you know it isn’t helping but keep circling it.\nSometimes you don’t notice because it’s become the default place your mind goes when something feels off.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"elgv4-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"elgv4-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"elgv4-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">So you’re not always choosing it cleanly.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"fo07f-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"fo07f-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"fo07f-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">But you keep giving it time, attention, and emotion.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"834d5-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"834d5-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"834d5-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">And what you keep feeding starts getting heavier.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"981dv-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"981dv-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"981dv-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">The more weight you give it, the more it starts shaping how your next move feels, what you notice, and what you do.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"1jrou-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"1jrou-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"1jrou-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">That’s where it starts taking more than it gives.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"b9p69-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"b9p69-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"b9p69-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">Not because it stopped being real.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"aa0rc-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"aa0rc-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"aa0rc-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">But because you kept feeding it after it had already shown you what to do with it.</span></span></div></div><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-16dba41\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; border: 0px solid black; color: rgb(231, 233, 234); display: inline; font-width: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; list-style: none; position: relative; overflow-wrap: break-word; min-width: 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2;\"><h1 class=\"longform-header-one-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"dad3r-0-0\" style=\"font-size: calc(21px); line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px;\"><div data-offset-key=\"dad3r-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"dad3r-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">It starts bending your next move</span></span></div></h1></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"8k9qj-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"8k9qj-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"8k9qj-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">A warning is supposed to change your behavior.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"nndf-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"nndf-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"nndf-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">If it shows you your setup is weak, fix the setup. If it shows you you’re rushing, slow down. If it shows you you’re avoiding the hard part, face it.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"c1oal-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"c1oal-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"c1oal-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">But when you keep feeding it, it starts making your next move worse.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"cslta-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"cslta-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"cslta-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">You see slow progress and move like the whole process is dying.\nYou feel behind, then rush so hard you lose the steadiness the process needed.\nYou catch a flaw, then spend more energy reacting to it than correcting it.\nYou notice one thing to fix, then redesign everything because the feeling got bigger than the problem.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"3qk60-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"3qk60-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"3qk60-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">None of this feels stupid from the inside.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"25fev-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"25fev-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"25fev-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">It feels serious.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"fbgq1-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"fbgq1-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"fbgq1-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">Careful.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"cppbc-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"cppbc-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"cppbc-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">Honest.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"h3e-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"h3e-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"h3e-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">It feels like staying close to reality.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"6pjg7-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"6pjg7-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"6pjg7-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">But now the warning isn’t just pointing at what needs to change.\nIt’s starting to interfere with your next move.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"36v2o-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"36v2o-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"36v2o-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">That’s the trap.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"59noa-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"59noa-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"59noa-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">The warning doesn’t have to be false to weaken you.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"bpbbb-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"bpbbb-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"bpbbb-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">It just has to start carrying more weight than the move it’s supposed to improve.</span></span></div></div><div dir=\"ltr\" class=\"css-146c3p1 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-37j5jr r-a023e6 r-rjixqe r-16dba41\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; border: 0px solid black; color: rgb(231, 233, 234); display: inline; font-width: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px; font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; list-style: none; position: relative; overflow-wrap: break-word; min-width: 0px; orphans: 2; widows: 2;\"><h1 class=\"longform-header-one-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"84kul-0-0\" style=\"font-size: calc(21px); line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px;\"><div data-offset-key=\"84kul-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"84kul-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">Use it before it uses you</span></span></div></h1></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"asouf-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"asouf-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"asouf-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">The question isn’t whether the warning is real.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"7o8e6-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"7o8e6-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"7o8e6-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">It probably is.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"8fp9c-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"8fp9c-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"8fp9c-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">What matters is what it already showed you.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"2icgf-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"2icgf-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"2icgf-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">Maybe the setup needs fixing. Maybe the pace needs slowing. Maybe the standard needs to become real enough to keep. Maybe the rep you keep avoiding needs to be done before you think about the whole system again.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"2ief7-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"2ief7-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"2ief7-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">That’s where this has to become action.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"7l4hm-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"7l4hm-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"7l4hm-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">Not more replaying.\nNot another night spent proving to yourself that the problem exists.\nNot more emotion spent circling the same point.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"ej5ha-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"ej5ha-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"ej5ha-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">Once the warning gives you the correction, act on it.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"gr0i-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"gr0i-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"gr0i-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">After that, more attention doesn’t make the correction stronger.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"116dt-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"116dt-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"116dt-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">It makes the warning stronger.</span></span></div></div><div class=\"longform-unstyled-narrow\" data-block=\"true\" data-editor=\"103hj\" data-offset-key=\"9u0ij-0-0\" style=\"white-space: pre-wrap; font-size: 17px; line-height: 28px; margin-bottom: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: TwitterChirp, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; orphans: 2; widows: 2; text-decoration-thickness: auto; text-decoration-style: solid;\"><div data-offset-key=\"9u0ij-0-0\" class=\"public-DraftStyleDefault-block public-DraftStyleDefault-ltr\" style=\"overflow: hidden; position: relative; direction: ltr;\"><span data-offset-key=\"9u0ij-0-0\"><span data-text=\"true\">And that’s how you keep strengthening what weakens you.</span></span></div></div>",
